properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 28 at 9:58PM CST until January 30 at 6:00AM CST by NWS Mobile AL
properties.description:
* WHAT...East winds 15 to 25 kt with gusts up to 30 kt and seas 4
to 6 ft expected.

* WHERE...Portions of the coastal waters of Alabama and
northwest Florida.

* WHEN...From 3 AM Wednesday to 6 AM CST Thursday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 3 AM WEDNESDAY TO 6 AM CST THURSDAY
